No. 254. North Shore Boom and Driving Company, Plaintiff in Error, v. Nicomen Boom Company. In error to the Supreme Court of the State of Washington. March 11, 1907. Mr. S. II. Piles for plaintiff in error. Mr. W. W. Cotton for defendant in error.

Dismissed with costs, on motion of Mr. S. H. Piles for the plaintiff in epror.
